{
"#tag"
:
[
"experimental"
]
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"⚠️ 实验性功能\n命令名、子命令结构、输出字段格式可能在后续版本变更，请勿用于生产脚本。\n欢迎在 https://github.com/x-cmd/x-cmd 提 issue 反馈。\n"
,
"en"
:
"⚠️ Experimental feature\nCommand name, subcommand structure, and output field formats may change in future releases — do not use in production scripts.\nFeedback welcome at https://github.com/x-cmd/x-cmd\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"stat 从 AI agent 会话日志中提取按 turn 粒度的结构化统计数据，用于成本核算和效率评估。\n一轮 turn = 从用户发送一条消息开始，到 AI 完成全部响应（含 tool call 循环）为止的完整过程。\n每个 turn 提取 12 个字段：input/output/thinking/cache token 数、API 调用次数、人类等待时长、human_ratio、human_message（人类输入文本，作为按任务类型聚合的语义锚点）等。\n"
,
"en"
:
"stat extracts per-turn structured statistics from AI agent session logs for cost accounting and efficiency review.\nA turn = from the user sending a message to the AI completing its full response (including tool-call loops).\nEach turn yields 12 fields: input/output/thinking/cache token counts, API call count, human wait duration, human_ratio, human_message (human prompt text, a semantic anchor for grouping by task type), etc.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"输出格式按受众选择：\n  text   人类可读：摘要 + 模型占比 + 引用明细 + 异常 + 亮点（默认）\n  brief  人类紧凑：一屏摘要 + 异常打标 + 趋势，适合终端/聊天窗口快速扫\n  tsv    给 AI agent：表头 + 制表符分隔，逐 turn 全字段，喂 awk/Excel\n  json   给 AI agent：JSON 数组，逐 turn 全字段，喂 jq/脚本\n"
,
"en"
:
"Pick output format by audience:\n  text   human-readable: summary + model usage + referenced turns + anomalies + highlights (default)\n  brief  human, compact: one-screen summary + labelled anomalies + trends, for terminal/chat windows\n  tsv    for AI agents: header + tab-separated, full per-turn fields, for awk/Excel\n  json   for AI agents: JSON array, full per-turn fields, for jq/scripts\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"会话定位两种方式（二选一）：\n  <file>          直接传 JSONL 文件路径\n  --session-id    传 session UUID，自动在 ~/.claude/projects/ 下查找\n                  优先 cwd 对应的 project 目录，找不到再全局扫描\n"
,
"en"
:
"Two ways to locate a session (mutually exclusive):\n  <file>          pass the JSONL file path directly\n  --session-id    pass a session UUID, auto-resolved under ~/.claude/projects/\n                  searches the cwd-derived project first, then all projects\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"成本估算单位为人民币（CNY）。内置定价覆盖 Claude / DeepSeek / GLM / MiniMax 主流模型。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Cost estimates are in CNY. Built-in pricing covers Claude / DeepSeek / GLM / MiniMax mainstream models.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"cross 子命令用于跨会话统计——一次解析多个 session 的 JSONL，输出按 turn 粒度的数据流。\n比 parse 多一列 session_id（溯源用），仅支持 tsv / json 格式，不支持人类可读报告（text / brief）。\nAI Agent 消费 tsv 后，按 human_message 做任务语义分类、再 awk 聚合。\nsession 选择方式：--session-id id1,id2,...（指定多个）或 --all（全部，可配合 --since / --until / --project 过滤）。\n"
,
"en"
:
"The cross subcommand provides cross-session statistics — parses multiple session JSONLs at once, emitting per-turn data.\nAdds a session_id column (for traceability) beyond parse's columns; only supports tsv / json (no text / brief).\nAI Agents consume the tsv output, classify by task via human_message, then aggregate with awk.\nSession selection: --session-id id1,id2,... (specific sessions) or --all (all sessions, with optional --since / --until / --project filters).\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"pricing 子命令输出内置模型定价表（CNY/百万 token）。AI Agent 做跨会话费用计算时，先调 pricing 获取价格，再结合 cross 的 token 数据算钱。\n"
,
"en"
:
"The pricing subcommand outputs the built-in model pricing table (CNY/million tokens). AI Agents call pricing to get unit prices, then multiply by cross token data to estimate costs.\n"
}
]
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent stat <subcmd> [options]"
]
,
"#subcmd:Parse"
:
[
"parse"
]
,
"#subcmd:Cross"
:
[
"cross"
]
,
"#subcmd:Pricing"
:
[
"pricing"
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id 16dee4f1-08ba-4964-a7b0-7c0073acc1ef"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 解析指定 session UUID 的 Claude Code 会话（人类可读报告）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Parse a Claude Code session by UUID (human-readable report)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude ~/.claude/projects/-Users-me-proj/session.jsonl"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 解析指定 JSONL 文件路径"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Parse a JSONL file by path"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id <uuid> --format brief"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 紧凑摘要，喂给 AI agent 当上下文"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Compact summary for feeding as AI agent context"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id <uuid> --format tsv > stats.tsv"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 导出 TSV 给 Excel/awk 处理"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Export TSV for Excel/awk processing"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id <uuid> --all"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 显示全部 turn（默认只显示被异常/亮点引用的）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Show all turns (default shows only those referenced)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat cross claude --all --since $(date -v-30d +%s) --format tsv"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 跨会话统计——获取近30天所有 turn 的 TSV 数据，AI Agent 按 human_message 分任务聚合"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Cross-session stats — get all turns from last 30 days as TSV; AI Agent groups by human_message for task-level aggregation"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat cross claude --session-id <uuid1>,<uuid2> --format json"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 跨会话统计——指定多个 session UUID，JSON 输出"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Cross-session stats — specify multiple session UUIDs, JSON output"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat cross claude --all --project='-Users-me-myproj' --format tsv | tail -n +2 | awk -F'\\t' '{input[$2]+=$3; output[$2]+=$4} END{for(m in input) printf \"%s\\t%d\\t%d\\n\",m,input[m],output[m]}'"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 跨会话统计——按项目过滤，awk 按模型聚合 token"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Cross-session stats — filter by project, awk aggregate by model"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat pricing --format tsv"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 输出内置模型定价表（CNY/百万token），供 AI Agent 计算费用"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Output built-in model pricing table (CNY/million tokens) for AI Agent cost calculation"
}
]
,
"parse"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"解析 AI agent 会话日志，按 turn 提取统计数据"
,
"en"
:
"Parse AI agent session log, extract per-turn statistics"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent stat parse <assistant> (<file> | --session-id <uuid>) [options]"
]
,
"#subcmd:Assistant"
:
[
"claude"
]
,
"claude"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"解析 Claude Code 会话 JSONL 文件"
,
"en"
:
"Parse Claude Code session JSONL file"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent stat parse claude (<file> | --session-id <uuid>) [options]"
]
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"Claude Code 会话 JSONL 文件路径（与 --session-id 二选一）"
,
"en"
:
"Claude Code session JSONL file path (alternative to --session-id)"
}
,
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__file"
}
,
"--session-id"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"Claude Code 会话 UUID，自动在 ~/.claude/projects/ 下查找（与 <file> 二选一）"
,
"en"
:
"Claude Code session UUID, auto-resolved under ~/.claude/projects/ (alternative to <file>)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"UUID 格式（8-4-4-4-12）"
,
"en"
:
"UUID format (8-4-4-4-12)"
}
}
}
,
"--offset"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"字节偏移，用于增量解析（跳过已处理部分）"
,
"en"
:
"Byte offset for incremental parsing (skip already-processed bytes)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"非负整数"
,
"en"
:
"Non-negative integer"
}
}
}
,
"--format"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"输出格式"
,
"en"
:
"Output format"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"text"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"人类可读，摘要 + 模型占比 + 明细 + 异常 + 亮点（默认）"
,
"en"
:
"Human-readable summary + model usage + table + anomalies + highlights (default)"
}
}
,
"brief"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"紧凑一屏摘要，给 AI agent 读：异常已打标 + 横向趋势"
,
"en"
:
"Compact one-screen summary for AI agents"
}
}
,
"tsv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"表头 + 制表符分隔，机器可读"
,
"en"
:
"Header + tab-separated, machine-readable"
}
}
,
"json"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"JSON 数组，每个元素一个 turn dict"
,
"en"
:
"JSON array, one turn dict per element"
}
}
}
}
,
"--all"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"明细表显示全部 turn（含 housekeeping/未被引用的；默认仅显示被异常或亮点引用的）"
,
"en"
:
"Show all turns in the detail table (default shows only those referenced by anomalies/highlights)"
}
}
,
"--no-human-message"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"不输出 human_message 字段（tsv 留空、json 为 null，列/字段结构不变）。分享或外发输出时使用——人类输入可能含代码、密钥、业务文本。"
,
"en"
:
"Suppress the human_message field (tsv empty cell, json null; column/field structure unchanged). Use when sharing/exporting output — human prompts may contain code, secrets, or business text."
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id 16dee4f1-08ba-4964-a7b0-7c0073acc1ef"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 按 UUID 解析（最常用，自动定位文件）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Parse by UUID (most common, auto-locates file)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude ./session.jsonl"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 按文件路径解析"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Parse by file path"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id <uuid> --format brief"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 给 AI 看的紧凑摘要"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Compact summary for AI consumption"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id <uuid> --format json | jq '.[].model'"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: JSON 输出 + jq 取每轮模型"
,
"en"
:
"Example: JSON output + jq to extract per-turn models"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id <uuid> --offset 1048576"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 增量解析（跳过前 1MB）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Incremental parse (skip first 1MB)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id <uuid> --all"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 显示全部 turn（含 housekeeping）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Show all turns (incl. housekeeping)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat parse claude --session-id <uuid> --format tsv --no-human-message"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 输出会分享/外发时，隐藏人类输入（含代码、密钥等）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Hide human prompts (code, secrets, etc.) when sharing/exporting output"
}
]
}
}
,
"cross"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"跨会话统计——解析多个 Claude Code 会话，串成带 session_id 列的逐 turn 数据流，供 AI Agent 按 human_message 做任务级聚合分析"
,
"en"
:
"Cross-session statistics — parse multiple Claude Code sessions into a single per-turn data stream with a session_id column, for AI Agent task-level aggregation by human_message"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent stat cross <assistant> (--session-id <ids> | --all) [options]"
]
,
"#subcmd:Assistant"
:
[
"claude"
]
,
"claude"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"解析多个 Claude Code 会话 JSONL 文件，输出带 session_id 的逐 turn 统计数据。仅支持 tsv / json 格式（不含人类可读报告），供 AI Agent 消费。"
,
"en"
:
"Parse multiple Claude Code session JSONL files, output per-turn statistics with session_id. Only tsv / json formats (no human-readable report); designed for AI Agent consumption."
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent stat cross claude (--session-id <id1,id2,...> | --all) [options]"
]
,
"--session-id"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"逗号分隔的会话 UUID 列表（与 --all 二选一）"
,
"en"
:
"Comma-separated session UUIDs (alternative to --all)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"逗号分隔的 UUID，如 \"id1,id2,id3\""
,
"en"
:
"Comma-separated UUIDs, e.g. \"id1,id2,id3\""
}
}
}
,
"--all"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"包含 ~/.claude/projects/ 下所有会话（与 --session-id 二选一）"
,
"en"
:
"Include all sessions under ~/.claude/projects/ (alternative to --session-id)"
}
}
,
"--since"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"Unix 时间戳（秒），仅包含首条记录时间 >= 此值的会话（需配合 --all）"
,
"en"
:
"Unix epoch seconds; only sessions with first timestamp >= this value (requires --all)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"Unix 秒级时间戳"
,
"en"
:
"Unix epoch seconds"
}
}
}
,
"--until"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"Unix 时间戳（秒），仅包含首条记录时间 < 此值的会话（需配合 --all）"
,
"en"
:
"Unix epoch seconds; only sessions with first timestamp < this value (requires --all)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"Unix 秒级时间戳"
,
"en"
:
"Unix epoch seconds"
}
}
}
,
"--project"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"按项目目录名精确过滤（需配合 --all）。目录名即 ~/.claude/projects/ 下的子目录名（工作路径 / 替换为 -）"
,
"en"
:
"Filter by exact project directory name (requires --all). Directory name = subdirectory under ~/.claude/projects/ (cwd with / replaced by -)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"项目目录名，以 - 开头（如 \"-Users-me-myproj\"），建议用 --project='...' 形式"
,
"en"
:
"Project dir name, starts with - (e.g. \"-Users-me-myproj\"); use --project='...' form"
}
}
}
,
"--format"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"输出格式（仅 tsv / json，不支持 text / brief）"
,
"en"
:
"Output format (tsv / json only; text / brief not supported)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"tsv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"表头 + 制表符分隔，末尾多一列 session_id"
,
"en"
:
"Header + tab-separated, with extra session_id column"
}
}
,
"json"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"JSON 数组，每个 turn 对象含 session_id"
,
"en"
:
"JSON array, each turn object includes session_id"
}
}
}
}
,
"--no-human-message"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"不输出 human_message 字段（tsv 留空、json 为 null，列/字段结构不变）。分享或外发输出时使用——人类输入可能含代码、密钥、业务文本。"
,
"en"
:
"Suppress the human_message field (tsv empty cell, json null; column/field structure unchanged). Use when sharing/exporting output — human prompts may contain code, secrets, or business text."
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat cross claude --all --since $(date -v-30d +%s) --format tsv"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 近30天全部 turn 的 TSV，AI Agent 按 human_message 分任务聚合"
,
"en"
:
"Example: All turns from last 30 days as TSV; AI Agent groups by human_message for task-level aggregation"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat cross claude --session-id <uuid1>,<uuid2> --format json"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 指定多个 session 输出 JSON"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Multiple sessions as JSON"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat cross claude --all --project='-Users-me-myproj' --since 1778700000 --format tsv"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 按项目 + 时间过滤"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Filter by project + time"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent stat cross claude --all --format tsv --no-human-message"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 外发时隐藏人类输入"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Hide human prompts when sharing output"
}
]
}
}
,
